Build-phase marker — while this file exists, agent sessions may edit core/
and .claude/ (kernel build, diffs approved in-session by Abhijeet).

DELETE THIS FILE at operational cutover (M1 shadow start). Hooks then
hard-deny agent writes to:
  core/  (config.py and all kernel modules)
  .claude/hooks/  .claude/settings.json
  rails/REGISTRY.md

The marker itself is never agent-writable (guardrails deny it even while it
exists), so removal is one-way from the agent's point of view.
